'''2016年6月伊斯坦堡爆炸案'''，是指發生於2016年6月7日，在[[土耳其|土耳其]][[伊斯坦堡|伊斯坦堡]][[法蒂赫|法蒂赫]]的一起[[炸彈|炸彈]]爆炸案。大約在當地時間([[UTC+3|UTC+3]])八時四十分左右<ref name=ntv>{{cite web|title=İstanbul Vezneciler'de polise bombalı araçla saldırı|url=http://www.ntv.com.tr/turkiye/istanbul-veznecilerde-polise-bombali-aracla-saldiri,LB3gLEIKrkytgcIBMaeM3w|publisher=NTV|accessdate=7 June 2016|language=tr|archive-date=2016-06-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160608185534/http://www.ntv.com.tr/turkiye/istanbul-veznecilerde-polise-bombali-aracla-saldiri%2cLB3gLEIKrkytgcIBMaeM3w|dead-url=no}}</ref>，一枚炸彈在市中心被引爆。此次襲擊的目標是一輛行進中載著[[警察|警察]]的[[巴士|巴士]]，當時該巴士正通過[[韋斯內奇勒區|韋斯內奇勒區]]（Vezneciler district）<ref>{{cite news|title=Istanbul: 'Deadly blast' hits police bus in Vezneciler|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-36466744|accessdate=6 June 2016|archive-date=2016-06-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160608222030/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-36466744|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Guzel|first1=Mehmet|title=Turkish official says bomb in Istanbul kills 11|url=http://bigstory.ap.org/article/366603b622bf423db8756226ed803762/state-tv-says-bomb-attack-targets-police-vehicle-istanbul|accessdate=6 June 2016|issue=7 June 2016|publisher=Associated Press|date=7 June 2016|archive-date=2016-06-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160608140508/http://www.bigstory.ap.org/article/366603b622bf423db8756226ed803762/state-tv-says-bomb-attack-targets-police-vehicle-istanbul|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。爆炸還造成了36人受傷<ref name=t24>{{cite web|title=İstanbul Vezneciler'de polis aracına bombalı saldırı, 7'si polis, 11 kişi hayatını kaybetti|url=http://t24.com.tr/haber/dha-istanbulda-veznecilerde-polis-aracina-bombali-saldiri-duzenlendi,344080|publisher=T24|accessdate=7 June 2016|language=tr|archive-date=2016-06-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160608151709/http://t24.com.tr/haber/dha-istanbulda-veznecilerde-polis-aracina-bombali-saldiri-duzenlendi,344080|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2016年6月10日，與[[庫爾德工人黨|庫爾德工人黨]]有關連的[[庫爾德自由之鷹|庫爾德自由之鷹]]發表聲明，表示襲擊是其成員所為。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.chinanews.com/gj/2016/06-10/7900141.shtml |title=“库尔德自由之鹰”宣称制造伊斯坦布尔袭击事件 |publisher=中新網 |date=2016-06-10 |accessdate=2016-06-10 |archive-date=2016-08-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160807134125/http://www.chinanews.com/gj/2016/06-10/7900141.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>

